Template: thinkfan/postinst-notice
Type: note
Description: thinkfan requires manual configuration before using.
 Please consult thinkfan(1) and thinkfan.conf(5) manual pages for more information.
 .
 Also, it is recommended to use the fan control interface provided by thinkpad_acpi kernel module. The option required for it to be operational is enabled automatically.
 .
 Please reboot your laptop for the configuration to take effect.
Description-zh_CN.UTF-8: thinkfan 需要手动配置才能使用。
 请阅读 thinkfan(1) 及 thinkfan.conf(5) 手册页来了解配置方式。
 .
 同时，我们推荐您使用 thinkpad_acpi 内核模块提供的接口控制风扇速度。提供风扇控制接口的选项已经自动启用。
 .
 请在配置完毕后重新启动您的笔记本电脑，以激活风扇控制功能。
